{
  "stem": "9489.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I did know nothing about farming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was in the army, and this they give me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "For the weekend I used to come and spend a good time, you know, parties-- girls, boys, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I kept it for a year, that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyways-- And you were still technically in the army?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Technically in the army on account they find out the Americans and the British and the French made a deal with the Germans to organize and invade Russia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this was very secret, so the top guys, they kept it in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they kept us without uniform, and they give us, you know, the cream.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And finally they got me, they poisoned-- eight guys of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE] made us a party, and they poison us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Me and my buddy survived on account we put in two fingers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew survival.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Two fingers we cut it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe we didn't get the real, you know, so much poison, but the rest, eight guys on the table, passed out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And even the floor-- later when we come in from the hospital, the floor, when we give it up, and the floor was all-- from our stomach, me and [?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Fadia ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I got a picture with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And since then I was suffering, and I didn't trust nobody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I give up everything, and I find out from-- in Wroclaw, this big concentration Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Jewish from Russia who survived, from Poland, and from there descended to Italy, from Italy over to Germany, from there they go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we were in Lublin, they brought us fresh soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lots of us got hit.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
